{"type": "article", "id": 20654, "title": "Nike 风行者夹克是如何诞生的？这组漫画告诉你", "description": "17 张图说完一件外套的前世今生。", "date": "2016-01-13T15:43:54Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 29, "name": "Top 15"}, {"id": 22032, "name": "Windrunner Jacket"}, {"id": 191, "name": "漫画"}, {"id": 27, "name": "Nike"}, {"id": 22033, "name": "Phil Knight"}], "category": 18, "author": 26306, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 88, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606134832Wo7TXsBrHYNAujCS.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">NIKE Windrunner Jacket 是 NIKE 的拳头产品之一。和 NIKE 的许多单品一样，不仅是运动场上的常客，也得到潮流人士的青睐，见诸于社交网络上的时髦街拍。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606134825lcPd43TXQs6gDveS.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606134825QBcxKdq904igkSbH.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"><span style=\"text-align:start;\">NIKE 将 </span><span style=\"text-align:start;\">2016 年定为「The year of the Windrunne」，并用一组美式漫画《The NIKE Windrunner: A Visual History》回顾了这款经典外套的诞生史。</span></span><span style=\"text-align:start;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">1975 年，NIKE 创始人 Phil Knight 和大学校友 Geoff Hollister 为 NIKE 赞助的运动员设计了一系列运动产品。不过他们很快注意到，运动员跑完步后经常是大汗淋漓，腥臭、汗湿的运动衣紧紧地贴在身上，别提有多难受了。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t他们决定从透气性、排汗功能入手，做一款即便是刮风下雨都能够派上用场的防水风雨衣。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606134826m6El58sOHr1GoSLM.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606134826h2OYneSRqM0bdHoB.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606134827ydSwupzngtPAf784.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061348271UAFvgY8GJ7ryu02.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606134827TgrpUv1z0Fq93Iwb.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060613482851XCJSsM4HruPBOA.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>1979 年，第一款 </span><span style=\"text-align:start;\">Windrunner Jacket 诞生了。这种</span><span style=\"text-align:start;\">尼龙外套的剪裁向下倾斜 26 度至胸部位置、上半部剪裁配合可防水的聚氨酯外层、下半部内藏透气小孔的设计，这些改进大大提升了排汗透气的功能。设计灵感据说是来自于太平洋沿岸的美国土著，他们用西洋杉树皮编织而成，用来抵挡风雨的斗篷。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606134828byhlaIpEV7OUmujk.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606134829tzECqQy91iWkUKFP.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">1984 年洛杉矶奥运会，58 名 NIKE 签约运动员取得了 65 块奖牌的骄人记录，</span><span style=\"text-align:start;\">Windrunner Jacket 一次又一次登上领奖台，曝光在无数闪光灯面前，</span><span style=\"text-align:start;\">Windrunner Jacket 很快流行起来。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606134829XbPjLvEoM6zSVwCg.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061348291HoMnfwDEjXpSbOC.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">随着 Hip-Hop 等街头文化的兴起，穿着 Windrunner Jacket 跳街舞或者玩街头极限运动也开始演变成一种趋势。为了顺应时代与潮流，Nike 对 Windrunner Jacket 加以升级改良，从日常运动穿着使用再到注重功能性，无论是款式设计还是面料的选取上都得到革新，至今 Nike Windrunner Jacket 系列仍然是年轻人青睐的服装款式。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060613483007pOCwVYQyDHmc53.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606134830U4GDramSAEzClLMN.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150525fk6WUcm8rAHpwVI2.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606134831SX7IP5uwL9hnm4ze.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606134831eqFcgyNUALIduoOj.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061348319DlEIohL7i2RYFun.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span>图片来自<a href=\"http://news.nike.com/news/the-nike-windrunner-a-visual-history\" target=\"_blank\"> NIKE</a></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}